{"id":249428,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/global-voices-委内瑞拉：阿穆艾炼油厂爆炸/","date":"2012-08-30T11:15:13Z","modified":"2012-08-30T11:15:13Z","title":"Global Voices | 委内瑞拉：阿穆艾炼油厂爆炸","content":"<p><p>八月廿五日清晨一点钟，法尔孔州胡迪瓦纳的阿穆艾炼油厂一座油槽发生<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.eluniversal.com/economia/120825/blast-at-venezuelas-major-oil-refinery-amuay\" href=\"http://www.eluniversal.com/economia/120825/blast-at-venezuelas-major-oil-refinery-amuay\">爆炸</a>。这次爆炸造成<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/business/refinery-explosion-in-venezuela-leaves-at-least-7-dead-dozens-injured-state-governor-says/2012/08/25/1c54ca7c-ee99-11e1-b624-99dee49d8d67_story.html\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/business/refinery-explosion-in-venezuela-leaves-at-least-7-dead-dozens-injured-state-governor-says/2012/08/25/1c54ca7c-ee99-11e1-b624-99dee49d8d67_story.html\">至少</a>廿六人死亡（法尔孔当地媒体报导卅五人死亡）和八十六人受伤。伤亡者多是玻利瓦尔国家卫队的成员。阿穆艾是委内瑞拉最重要的炼油厂，也是世界五大炼油厂之一。</p>\n<p>意外发生的原因目前还不清楚。</p>\n<p>一名住在附近的医生 Gabriela Gonzalez (<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/gabriela2400/\" href=\"https://twitter.com/gabriela2400/\">@gabriela2400</a>) 告诉委内瑞拉记者 Nelson Bocaranda，炼油厂的警报在意外发生前半小时曾响过但又被关闭。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/gabriela2400/status/239380521338142720\" href=\"https://twitter.com/gabriela2400/status/239380521338142720\">@gabriela2400</a>：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/NelsonBocaranda\" href=\"https://twitter.com/NelsonBocaranda\">@NelsonBocaranda</a> 12:30 警报响起，又很快被关闭。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>副总统埃利亚斯．哈瓦（Elías Jaua）和<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Petr%C3%B3leos_de_Venezuela\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Petr%C3%B3leos_de_Venezuela\">委内瑞拉石油公司</a>（Pdvsa）总裁拉法叶．拉米雷兹（Rafael Ramírez）目前正在阿穆艾，他们<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.eluniversal.com/nacional-y-politica/120825/declaraciones-de-rafael-ramirez-y-elias-jaua-tras-explosion-en-amuay\" href=\"http://www.eluniversal.com/nacional-y-politica/120825/declaraciones-de-rafael-ramirez-y-elias-jaua-tras-explosion-en-amuay\">宣布</a>有关当局会在炼油厂努力到火势扑灭为止，而消防队的工作也包括处理市民回报的烟雾。此外他们保证政府会负责承担所有的损失。</p>\n<p>網絡上流传的照片和影片中此地看起来比较发生过地震而不是爆炸。<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.noticias24.com/fotos/noticia/1487/la-tragedia-de-amuay-vista-por-las-imagenes-exclusivas-del-fotografo-hector-silva/\" href=\"http://www.noticias24.com/fotos/noticia/1487/la-tragedia-de-amuay-vista-por-las-imagenes-exclusivas-del-fotografo-hector-silva/\">Noticias 24</a> 收集了从悲剧发生时便在现场的摄影师 Héctor Silva 的照片。</p>\n<p>Youtube 上有数段民众自行拍摄上传的爆炸事件影片：</p>\n<p> </p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p>La Verdad 报（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/laverdadweb\" href=\"https://twitter.com/laverdadweb\">@laverdadweb</a>）<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/laverdadweb/status/239399765845098498\" href=\"https://twitter.com/laverdadweb/status/239399765845098498\">报导</a>炼油厂周遭区域仍可闻到丙烷类似催泪瓦斯的气味。</p>\n<p>José Luis Cova R（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/JLCova/\" href=\"http://twitter.com/JLCova/\">@JLCova</a>）在推特上说：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/JLCova/status/239394103060729857\" href=\"http://twitter.com/JLCova/status/239394103060729857\">@JLCova</a>：丙烷爆炸的影响半径是毁灭性的。胡迪瓦纳入口周遭一切都被摧毁了。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>他也报告一间在委内瑞拉被称作 bodegones 的食物和酒类饮料店遭到洗劫：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/JLCova/status/239400361859895296\" href=\"https://twitter.com/JLCova/status/239400361859895296\">@JLCova</a>：胡迪瓦纳入口的 Lizolca bodegon 遭到洗劫！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>大部分爆炸中的伤者被送到了 Calles Sierra 医院，根据 Gabriela Gonzalez（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/gabriela2400/\" href=\"http://twitter.com/gabriela2400/\">@gabriela2400</a>）的报导此处没有足够的补给：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/gabriela2400/status/239376754156900353\" href=\"http://twitter.com/gabriela2400/status/239376754156900353\">@gabriela2400</a>：Calles Sierra 医院需要：抗生素、血浆、血液、止痛药、吗啡、镇痛药、纱布、乳酸林格液、生理食盐水。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>总统乌戈．查维兹（Hugo Chávez）<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-19378657\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-19378657\">宣布</a>为阿穆艾的死伤者进行为期三天的全国哀悼。</p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Portnoy\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E5%A7%94%E5%86%85%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%EF%BC%9A%E9%98%BF%E7%A9%86%E8%89%BE%E7%82%BC%E6%B2%B9%E5%8E%82%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F30%2F11395%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F30%2F11395%2F&#038;desc=%E5%A7%94%E5%86%85%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%EF%BC%9A%E9%98%BF%E7%A9%86%E8%89%BE%E7%82%BC%E6%B2%B9%E5%8E%82%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F30%2F11395%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F30%2F11395%2F&#038;text=%E5%A7%94%E5%86%85%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%EF%BC%9A%E9%98%BF%E7%A9%86%E8%89%BE%E7%82%BC%E6%B2%B9%E5%8E%82%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F30%2F11395%2F&#038;title=%E5%A7%94%E5%86%85%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%EF%BC%9A%E9%98%BF%E7%A9%86%E8%89%BE%E7%82%BC%E6%B2%B9%E5%8E%82%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submi